queries.sql: SELECT nodemcu.IdNodemcu, DATE_FORMAT(caudal.fecha, '%Y-%m-%d') AS Fecha, SUM(caudal.caudal) AS caudal, nodemcu.Nombre FROM nodemcu JOIN caudal ON nodemcu.IdNodemcu = caudal.IdNodemcu WHERE nodemcu.IdUsuario = '33' AND nodemcu.IdNodemcu = 'DE32A7B02A8C' GROUP BY nodemcu.IdNodemcu, caudal.Fecha;
